FCC May Delist Cementos Portland Valderrivas Unit, Negocio Says

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-02-23T13:45:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/fcc-may-delist-cementos-portland-valderrivas-unit-negocio-says.html
Spanish builder Fomento de
Construcciones & Contratas SA may buy the shares it doesn’t
already own in its  Cementos Portland Valderrivas SA  unit,
 Negocio  reported, citing unidentified people in financial
markets.  FCC owns 69.7 percent of Cementos  Portland , Negocio said.
It could offer 20 euros a share, or 229 million euros ($314
million), to buy the stock it doesn’t own in the cement company
and then proceed to delist it, the newspaper added.  A spokesman for FCC declined to comment on the report when
contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net  